      • validateGuestForm

        protected boolean validateGuestForm​(java.lang.Class<? extends generated.GuestRequest> clazz)

        Reason: guest process rely on EditGuest***Handler which throws forbidden if Form type cannot be published in target workspace.

      • getSignupWorkspaceSet

        public java.util.Set<com.jalios.jcms.workspace.Workspace> getSignupWorkspaceSet​(com.jalios.jcms.Member member,
                                                                                boolean includeModel,
                                                                                boolean includeClosed)
        Returns a Workspace set where given member can signup a Guest.

        As of current implementation, it will return Workspaces:

        • where given member can manage Members (ie, is space admin, or has global or workspace Edit Member ACL
        • that have at least one visible Group
        • which is a CollaborativeSpace
        Parameters:
        member - the Member to return its "Signup" Workspace set
        includeModel - weither to include model workspaces or not
        includeClosed - weither to include closed workspaces or not
        Returns:
        a Set of Workspaces.
        Since:
        csp-4.1
